DESCRIPTION:<u></u>Too Cold for a Scheduled Ride. Those who nevertheless wi
 th to ride are welcome to choose a suitable route.<br><br><span>This group 
 emphasizes earlier\, moderate-paced rides with routes planned in advance an
 d posted on the ride calendar. This is a no drop ride\, but not a beginner'
 s ride.  Expect an overall average moving speed of 12 - 15 mph.  Distances 
 vary from 20 to a little over 30 miles.  Early season rides will be at the 
 lower end of the distance scale.  During colder weather the ride departs at
  1:00pm.  </span><br><br>Non-members should sign up for a <a href="https://
 secure.getmeregistered.com/get_information.php?event_id=136627" target="_bl
 ank">free trial membership</a>\, good for up to three rides\, and which inc
 ludes electronically signing a liability waiver\, prior to participation.<b
 r><br><br><u></u>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260316T011842Z
LOCATION:Bryan Park Parking Lot\, S Woodlawn Ave\, Bloomington\, IN 47401\,
  USA
SEQUENCE:11
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Early Birds - Too Cold
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
