BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Bloomington": "https://www.visitbloomington.com/event/the-shape-of-water-%7c-jorgensen-guest-filmmaker-series-transfixed%3a-michael-shannon-on-screen/58043/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visitbloomington
SUMMARY:The Shape of Water | Jorgensen Guest Filmmaker Series\, Transfixed
 : Michael Shannon on Screen
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260324T040000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260325T035959Z
UID:event-58043@visitbloomington.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://assets.simpleviewinc.com/simpleview/imag
 e/upload/crm/bloomington/The-Shape-of-Water-1920x1080_AF2E5D1E-C430-E1DB-4
 59D081CC6A048DE_af3ae456-acd8-87cc-48be5370c49895cb.jpg
DESCRIPTION:From master storyteller Guillermo del Toro\, The Shape of Wate
 r is an otherworldly fable\, set against the backdrop of Cold War-era Amer
 ica circa 1962. In the hidden high-security government laboratory where sh
 e works\, lonely Elisa (Sally Hawkins) is trapped in a life of isolation. 
