DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: PhotoFocus Photography Club\n\nDuring our weekly me
 etings as PhotoFocus\, we host a number of exciting group-focused events a
 nd competitions. Among these opportunities\, we hold editing games (Edit-O
 ffs)\, photography presentations\, crtique nights\, movie viewings\, jeopa
 rdy competitions\, and photo exchanges between members. These weekly meeti
 ngs are the backbone of our organization\, and present an opportunity for 
 the club members and leaders to socialize\, grow in photographic skill\, d
 evelop editing knowledge\, and gather helpful feedback from peers. We meet
  for one hour per week in order to maintain a regular communal atmosphere.
LOCATION:Woodburn Hall\, WH 111
