DESCRIPTION:Just like mosaics\, our stories are made up of many pieces. J
 oin La Casa's Queer initiative as we create DIY mosaic picture frames and
  celebrate the beauty in every fragment of who we are.Materials and snack
 s provided. Bring a photo or make the frame for a future memory.&#160\;La
  Casa Queer Initiative creates an inclusive and affirming space for LGBTQ
 + students to connect\, find support\, and build community.
