SUMMARY:Lotus At IU Call Out
DESCRIPTION:Date: March 25\nTime: 6 to 7 p.m.\nLocation: IMU Maple Room\n  \nHelp Start the Lotus Student Club at IU\nAre you passionate about music\, culture\, community\, and creativity? \nThe Lotus Education & Arts Foundation is looking for Indiana University students who want to help launch the official Lotus Student Club at IU. \nThis student-led group will help connect campus life with the global arts community through opportunities like: \n\nsupporting the Lotus World Music & Arts Festival\nworking with artists from around the world\nhelping produce cultural events and workshops\ngaining hands-on experience in arts\, media\, and event production\nbuilding a welcoming community around music\, culture\, and creative exchange\n\nWhether you love music\, arts\, production\, storytelling\, or just meeting interesting people from around the world — there’s a place for you here. \nThis is a chance to shape the club from the ground up and create something meaningful on campus. \nInterested in helping start it?\nReach out or join our interest meeting: Let’s build something beautiful together.
URL:https://www.lotusfest.org/event/lotus-at-iu-call-out/
LOCATION:Indiana Memorial Union\, 900 E 7th St\, Bloomington\, 47405\, United States
CATEGORIES:Free Event
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://www.lotusfest.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Call-Out-Meeting-1.webp
