DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Panhellenic Association\n\nPanhellenic is excited t
 o host their first-ever study tables! These will be bi-weekly sessions fro
 m 6-8 p.m. on Wednesdays hosted for women to collaborate with others in si
 milar fields or majors.&nbsp\; &nbsp\; WHAT:&nbsp\; Each specific session 
 will be dedicated to a specific class or exam that is occurring later in t
 he week or the following week. For example\, if there is an accounting exa
 m the following week\, we will host a study table specifically for that ac
 counting exam! &nbsp\; HOW: Each chapter's academic affairs/learning conta
 ct in their chapter will post what exam/class the study session is for\, a
 nd any Panhellenic woman is welcome to come. Please keep an eye out for th
 eir messages for room updates each week! &nbsp\; WHEN: Every other Wednesd
 ay starting 03/25\, from 6-8 p.m. The location for each table will be sent
  out via your Academic Affairs liaison in each chapter! &nbsp\; We look fo
 rward to seeing you there :)
