DESCRIPTION:Come see the beautiful watercolor artworks of Bloomington Wate
 rcolor Society at Gallery Mortgage. Our works this year will be encompassi
 ng the theme "America the Beautiful". The artists will display their inter
 pretations of America's beauty over the last 250 years in original waterco
 lor paintings. Two receptions will be held Friday\, February 6\, 2026 Open
 ing Day of Show & Reception at Gallery Mortgage 5-8pmAndFriday\, March 6\,
  2026 March Reception at Gallery Mortgage 5-8 PM Regular Gallery hours wil
 l be 9am - 5pm Monday - Friday through March 27th. A portion of sales will
  benefit Teachers' Warehouse.
