DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Student Involvement and Leadership Center\n\nJoin u
 s for the Student Involvement and Leadership Center&rsquo\;s&nbsp\; Bridge
 work Series \, a monthly leadership and organizational development series 
 designed to help students strengthen their team-building skills\, understa
 nd group dynamics\, and become agents of change within their organizations
  and communities. Each session will center around a key aspect of how grou
 ps work&mdash\;from communication and collaboration to culture-building an
 d creating sustainable impact&mdash\;through interactive activities and re
 al-world leadership scenarios. This 8-event series (spanning the academic 
 year) provides an engaging space for students to connect across campus\, l
 earn the foundations of effective teamwork\, and explore how they can cont
 ribute to meaningful change. Whether you're leading a student org\, suppor
 ting a team\, or just getting started\, Bridgework offers practical tools 
 and powerful insights to help you build better bridges&mdash\;bet
LOCATION:IMU Frangipani Room 
URL:https://iub.campuslabs.com/engage/event/11321015
