DESCRIPTION:FRIDAY\, MARCH 27All events at IU Innovates  Note: Additional
  events are on Thursday and Saturday. See Website for details.&#160\;CONF
 ERENCE WEBSITE (https://blogs.iu.edu/jsominnovation/algorhythms-the-world
 -of-music-and-ai/) |&#160\;Sign Up To Attend &gt\; (https://forms.office.
 com/r/4QgGSdDfzp) | See Who the Participants Are &gt\; (https://blogs.iu.
