X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Sycamore Land Trust": "https://sycamorelandtrust.org/2026/02/the-hidden-world-of-lichens-with-gillian-harris/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:sycamore_land_trust
SUMMARY:The Hidden World of Lichens with Gillian Harris
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260327T090000
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260327T113000
UID:b4a8d332e6e97867d84898dd38a88ecb@sycamorelandtrust.org
DESCRIPTION:Discover the Hidden World of Lichens\, led by naturalist and a
 rtist Gillian Harris! Lichens\, which are a unique partnership between fun
 gi and algae or cyanobacteria\, are more than just “mossy stuff” on tr
 ees and rocks\; they’re fascinating indicators of air quality\, habitat 
 diversity\, and ecosystem health. As we hike\, we’ll observe these often
 -overlooked organisms in their many forms and learn about their biology\, 
 where they live\, and why they matter.
LOCATION:The Laura Hare Nature Preserve at Downey Hill
URL:https://sycamorelandtrust.org/2026/02/the-hidden-world-of-lichens-with
 -gillian-harris/
X-SOURCE:Sycamore Land Trust
END:VEVENT
