SUMMARY:Brown Bag Talk: CoRSAL Lab Year in Review
DESCRIPTION:CoRSAL will present its 2025 activities as a digital language
  archive\, highlighting its curation of linguistic fieldwork from Central
  India (Munda languages) and from Northeast India and Thailand (Tibeto-Bu
 rman languages). The team will also report on skills developed across lan
 guage science and library and information science through this work.    &
 #160\;
