DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Asian American Association at Indiana University\n\
 nCelebrate spring and test your luck at the Lucky Bamboo Bash! Join fellow
  freshmen for a fun night of games and activities. Decorate your own lucky
  bamboo\, try a mystery red envelope\, spin the trivia wheel\, and play ca
 rd and dice games. Stop by the photo booth for Polaroids\, add your goals 
 to the Luck Wall for good fortune this semester\, and wear green to join t
 he festive theme. Come hang out\, meet other freshmen\, and see how lucky 
 you are!🍀
