SUMMARY:Dramatic Entanglements: Ecologies and Encounters on the Premodern
  Stage
DESCRIPTION:A two-day symposium exploring eco-social entanglements on the
  premodern stage. Featuring short talks and performances by invited schol
 ars\, faculty\, and students\, the event examines how early drama stages 
 environmental\, social\, and political encounters—and what those overla
 pping ecologies can tell us now.  Sponsored by the College Arts and Human
 ities Institute and the Environmental Futures Initiative.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  A two-day symposium exploring eco-socia
 l entanglements on the premodern stage. Featuring short talks and perform
 ances by invited scholars\, faculty\, and students\, the event examines h
 ow early drama stages environmental\, social\, and political encounters
 and what those overlapping ecologies can tell us now.</p><p>  Sponsored 
 by the College Arts and Humanities Institute and the Environmental Future
 s Initiative.</p>
