DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Live Reality Games @ IU\n\nLive Reality Games @ IU 
 brings the hit game show The Floor to campus! 🧠🔥 Step onto the floor
  and put your knowledge to the test in a fast-paced\, competitive trivia e
 xperience where every square counts. Participants will face off in head-to
 -head challenges across a variety of categories\, battling to claim territ
 ory and outlast the competition. With over $200 in prizes on the line\, th
 e stakes are high and the energy is even higher. Whether you&rsquo\;re a t
 rivia master or just in it for the fun\, The Floor @ IU is your chance to 
 compete\, win\, and show what you&rsquo\;ve got. Come play\, come watch\, 
 and see who takes control of the floor! APPLICATION &amp\; FULL WRITEUP IN
