 d with the Maurer School of Law\, IU Innovates\, Music Tectonics\, and th
 e AI+Digital Futures Team\,...
LOCATION:Sweeney Hall\, IU Jacobs School of Music\,1201 E 3rd St\, Bloomi
 ngton\, IN 47405\, USA
