 the City of Bloomington's Cool Corridors Project.\n\nVolunteers can sign-up
  here: https://www.canopybloomington.org/upcoming-plantings\n\nAbout Canopy
 Bloomington: A social impact organization created to maximize Bloomington's
  tree canopy and sustainably manage Bloomington's urban forest for trees' m
 any environmental\, health\, economic\, and social benefits\, with a focus 
 on tree equity and community engagement.\n\nContact: Jon Vickers\nEmail: co
 mmunity@canopybloomington.org\nPhone: 269-876-1461
