 18b65e-23a5-402c-8297-3307d89183b5eaf6d14d-de7a-45fd-9106-82eecec0fb8f.png
DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Student Involvement and Leadership Center\n\nJoin u
 s for the Student Involvement and Leadership Center's&nbsp\; Leadership Co
 mpass Series \, a monthly leadership development series designed to help s
 tudents grow across the 8 Student Leadership Competency domains. Each sess
 ion will focus on one core leadership area&mdash\;ranging from self-awaren
 ess to civic responsibility&mdash\;through interactive workshops and hands
 -on activities. This 8-workshop series (spanning the academic year) provid
 es a dynamic space for students to build confidence\, sharpen their skills
 \, and connect with peers who are passionate about personal and community 
 growth. Whether you're new to leadership or already involved on campus\, t
 he SILC Leadership Compass &nbsp\;offers practical tools and meaningful co
 nversations to elevate your leadership journey&mdash\;one domain at a time
 . &nbsp\; ***Lunch is provided for participants from 12:00pm-1:00pm on all
  dates*** &nbsp\; 📅 March 28th\, 2026 ⏰ 10:00 AM &ndash\; 3:00 PM
LOCATION:IMU Club Hub
