SUMMARY:Banff Film Festival World Tour 2 Day Pass
DTSTART;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260328T190000
DTEND;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260328T220000
UID:260203CsUhLE2fBU-lTBwgH7_QoA
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://citysparkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/p
 ortalimages/portalimages/lpWCo-qltk2-MR7S1nUjUg.large.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Banff Centre Mountain Film Festival World Tour is coming to B
 loomington at 7pm on March 27th and 28th\, 2026! Presenting Partners: Rab 
 and Banff & Lake Louise Tourism. Brought to you by: IU Outdoor Adventures.
 \n\nBanff Centre Mountain Film and Book Festival is one of the largest and
  most prestigious mountain festivals in the world! Hot on the heels of the
  Festival that is held every fall in beautiful Banff\, Alberta\, the Banff
  Centre Mountain Film Festival World Tour hits the road. With stops planne
 d in over 600 communities and more than 40 countries across the globe\, th
 e Banff World Tour celebrates amazing achievements in outdoor storytelling
  and filmmaking worldwide.\n\nFrom the over 400 entries submitted to the F
 estival competition each year\, award-winners and audience favorites are a
 mong the films that are carefully selected to play in theatres around the 
 world. Traveling to remote vistas\, analyzing topical environmental issues
 \, and bringing audiences up-close and personal with adrenaline-packed act
 ion sports the 2025/2026 World Tour is an exhilarating and provocative exp
 loration of the mountain world.\n\nJoin IU Outdoor Adventures when Banff C
 entre Mountain Film Festival World Tour brings the spirit of outdoor adven
 ture to Bloomington\, at the Buskirk Chumley Theater on March 27th and 28t
 h at 7pm \\(doors 6pm\\). Visit outdoors.iu.edu for film specifics. For in
 formation contact IU Outdoor Adventures and Nicci Brown at brownnc@iu.edu 
 Film programs will be posted as soon as possible. Stay tuned!\n\nFor more 
 information about IU Outdoor Adventures\, check us out at: outdoors.iu.edu
  @iu\\_outdooradventures on Instagram\n\nFor more information about the Ba
 nff Centre Mountain Film Festival World Tour\, check them out at: @BanffMt
 nFest Facebook: BanffMountainFilmFestival \\#banffworldtour
LOCATION:Buskirk Chumley Theater
URL:https://cityspark.com/calendar/#/details/banff-film-festival-world-tou
 r-2-day-pass/17993128/2026-03-28T19
X-SOURCE:CitySpark Bloomington
END:VEVENT
