DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Bring Your Own Business\n\nCalling all savvy shoppe
 rs and student vendors! BYOB @ IU welcomes all students to showcase their 
 businesses at our bi-monthly events\, currently held at Dunn Meadow or ind
 oors in the IMU. While sellers must be IU students\, our events are open t
 o the wider Bloomington community. You&rsquo\;ll find a diverse range of s
 tudent-run businesses offering everything from vintage clothing and jewelr
 y to art prints\, plants\, and crochet items. Set up your table\, set your
  prices\, and engage with various shoppers. Our events highlight the creat
 ivity and entrepreneurial spirit of our members while providing invaluable
  real-world experience in marketing\, negotiating\, and customer interacti
 on. BYOB @ IU is more than just an organization&mdash\;it's a movement ded
 icated to empowering the next generation of entrepreneurs\, helping them b
 ring their ideas to life and connect with a broader audience. Follow us on
  Instagram (@byob.iu) to register for events and stay updated o
