SUMMARY:Life Skills Workshop Series: Healthcare Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Healthcare can feel confusing. This workshop will break down 
 the basics of accessing care\, preparing for appointments\, communicating
  with providers\, and finding reliable health resources. Whether you're m
 anaging your own healthcare for the first time or just want to feel more 
 confident in medical settings\, we've got tools and tips to help you take
  charge of your well-being.  &#160\;  All Indiana University events\, gro
 ups\, activities\, and educational\, cultural\, and historical observance
 s welcome all IU students and other members of the Indiana University com
 munity.
