 kshop will break down the basics of accessing care\, preparing for appoin
 tments\, communicating with providers\, and finding reliable health resou
 rces. Whether you're managing your own healthcare for the first time or j
 ust want to feel more confident in medical settings\, we've got tools and
  tips to help you take charge of your well-being.</p><p>  &#160\;</p><p> 
  All Indiana University events\, groups\, activities\, and educational\, 
 cultural\, and historical observances welcome all IU students and other m
 embers of the Indiana University community.</p>
