 E0_0cb923ca-bd4c-b860-7ad66b1a7050cd77.png
DESCRIPTION:John Wood Jr.\, National Ambassador of Braver Angels talks abo
 ut American identity\, political polarization\, and the framing of these i
 ssues in the broader context of America’s 250th Anniversary. Please join
  the Political and Civic Engagement (PACE) program in the honor of hosting
  John Wood Jr.\, National Ambassador of Braver Angels\, for an impeccably 
 pertinent talk on American identity\, political polarization\, and the fra
 ming of these issues in the broader context of America’s 250th Anniversa
