SUMMARY:Confident Conversations: Food\, Metabolism\, and Cancer Risk
DESCRIPTION:How do the foods we eat\, our metabolism\, and emerging weigh
 t-loss medications shape cancer risk? Join us for an evidence-based commu
 nity conversation exploring:Nutrition patterns linked to cancer preventio
 n  How metabolic health influences cancer risk  What GLP-1 medications (s
 uch as Ozempic and Wegovy) do - and what current research shows  Food acc
 ess\, affordability\, and equity    The evening includes expert discussio
 n\, audience Q&amp\;A\, community resource tables\, and a short interacti
 ve line-dance demonstration\, "Move for Your Metabolism."
