 ht/168/crop/1/src_region/0\,0\,598\,362/30435_ChenLec.rev.1773149433.png
X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  Please join the IAUNRC in welcoming Dr. Chen S
 u\, visiting scholar from Inner Mongolia University\, for a guest lecture
  on Sasanian and Persian iconography.&#160\;\n</p>
