  maybe food. We'll see.&nbsp\; Whether you're only watching because you th
 ink Colby is hot\, or you're excited to see Cirie lose for the eighth time
 \, our event is open to Survivor fans new and old! Great way to meet fun p
 eople and a good hang on a Wednesday night.
