SUMMARY:WEBINAR: Leading with AI\, Influence Info Session
DESCRIPTION:Influence is how leaders get things done\, especially when th
 ey don't have the authority over the people they need to move. In this ex
 ecutive education course on influence\, AI is used to strengthen your abi
 lity to persuade\, align stakeholders\, and mobilize teams. You'll learn 
 how to use AI to sharpen messaging\, rehearse conversations\, and stress-
 test strategies.  With Kelley's Executive Education webinar\, Leading wit
 h AI: Influence\, you'll gain the knowledge of utilizing AI tools for you
 r personal and professional growth with AI-enabled performance.  ENROLL I
 N THE COURSE: https://kelley-school-of-business-executive-education.mysho
 pify.com/collections/leading-with-ai-series/products/leading-with-ai-infl
 uence
