 f Art and a scholar of American Art History. As director\, Besaw oversees
  all facets of the museum's strategy\, operations\, and engagement\, incl
 uding exhibitions\, collections\, teaching partnerships\, and public prog
 ramming. <a href="https://artmuseum.indiana.edu/about/staff/_director/bes
