 10194f-a637-42ab-a91d-617d7087303c18b9c5dc-c2d6-46ce-8969-74c25c3e7ac3.png
DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Balance at Kelley\n\nBalance at Kelley is a club fo
 cused on raising awareness for mental health and being a safe and fun comm
 unity for Kelley students. Many meetings\, we start with a discussion abou
 t a mental health topic before moving into an activity that ranges from ga
 mes/crafts/competitions/conversations and more. These activities are desig
 ned to help us form bonds with each other. Other meetings are designed to 
 help you navigate being a Kelley student - connecting you with resources a
 nd advice to help you with your academics\, career search\, and mental wel
 lbeing. Come have fun with us while learning how to improve your mental he
 alth and prosper as a Kelley student!
