DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Ski and Snowboard Club at Indiana University\n\nAll
  students are welcome to join Ski and Snowboard Club at IU at any point in
  the year\, no previous ski or ride experience necessary! Our weekly commi
 ttee meetings are a fun way to meet other club members and the students on
  the executive committee while learning about all our year round events an
 d activities - social events\, co-ed intramural sports\, Polar Plunge for 
 Special Olympics\, supporting SKI women&rsquo\;s Little 500 cycling team\,
