DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Black in Business\n\nOverview Black in Business is 
 partnering with the American Red Cross to host a campus wide blood drive f
 ocused on increasing representation from minority student organizations an
 d expanding access to life saving donations. This event will take place in
  February or March. The exact date and location are still being confirmed.
  We will secure the location from 12 to 8\, and the active donation window
  will run from 3 to 7. There is also interest in making this a multi day d
 rive to maximize impact. Event Purpose &bull\; Promote equitable access to
  blood donation &bull\; Mobilize minority led organizations across IU &bul
 l\; Strengthen collaboration between Black in Business and campus partners
  &bull\; Deliver a high impact service project centered on community well 
 being
