X-LIVEWHALE-TYPE:events
X-LIVEWHALE-ID:2154917
X-LIVEWHALE-TIMEZONE:America/New_York
X-LIVEWHALE-CONTACT-INFO:<p>\n  Katie Beck&#160\;<br />\n  Director of Ad
 vancement\, Conservation Law Center&#160\;<br />\n  <a href="mailto:katbe
 ck@iu.edu">katbeck@iu.edu</a>\n</p>
