DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260412T120000
UID:3fa88c5fee2de9cd21b12814b5427c2c@sycamorelandtrust.org
DESCRIPTION:Join native plant and fungi guru David Mow for a guided tour o
 f Porter West Preserve in Monroe County to celebrate the emerging diversit
 y of life along the forest floor. This preserve features oak-hickory fores
 ted upland areas with carpets of wildflowers as well as sinkholes and inte
 resting rock outcroppings.
