 , dance\, and have a blast! On Tuesday\, April 15\, 2026\, Union Board Min
 d &amp\; Body is teaming up with Pulse Dance Club to bring you Move &amp\;
  Groove &ndash\; Hip Hop Cardio Class\, a high-energy\, one-hour hip hop c
 ardio workout in Alumni Hall. Led by members of Pulse Dance Club\, this cl
 ass is designed for all levels\, whether you're a seasoned dancer or just 
 someone who loves moving their body\, everyone is welcome on the dance flo
 or. We encourage you to please RSVP before the event.&nbsp\; Join us from 
 7:00&ndash\;8:00 PM to take a break from the stress of the week\, let loos
 e\, and get your heart pumping to some great music. This is the perfect op
 portunity to step away from the books\, have some fun\, and end your Tuesd
 ay night on a high note. Snacks and refreshments will be provided\, so all
  you have to do is show up and move! All Indiana University events\, group
 s\, activities\, and educational\, cultural\, and historical observances w
 elc
