SUMMARY:Mamma Mia! | Pop Music(als)!
DESCRIPTION:Bride-to-be Sophie (Amanda Seyfried) has just one wish to mak
 e her wedding perfect: to have her father walk her down the aisle. Now sh
 e just has to figure out who he is! Join the laughter and fun of this irr
 esistibly charming musical celebration of mothers\, daughters\, fathers\,
  true loves lost\, and the romantic possibilities of what can happen on a
  magical Greek island when you throw a little (a lotta) ABBA in the mix! 
 Academy Award-winner Meryl Streep leads an all-star cast\, including Pier
 ce Brosnan\, Colin Firth\, Stellan Skarsgård\, and Dominic Cooper. Based
  on the Broadway smash-hit and brimming with all the infectious ABBA song
 s we know and love. [108 min\; comedy\, musical\; English and Greek with 
 English subtitles]
