 s just one wish to make her wedding perfect: to have her father walk her 
 down the aisle. Now she just has to figure out who he is! Join the laught
 er and fun of this irresistibly charming musical celebration of mothers\,
  daughters\, fathers\, true loves lost\, and the romantic possibilities o
 f what can happen on a magical Greek island when you throw a little (a lo
 tta) ABBA in the mix! Academy Award-winner Meryl Streep leads an all-star
  cast\, including Pierce Brosnan\, Colin Firth\, Stellan Skarsgård\, and
  Dominic Cooper. Based on the Broadway smash-hit and brimming with all th
 e infectious ABBA songs we know and love. [108 min\; comedy\, musical\; E
 nglish and Greek with English subtitles]</p>
