DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260417T193000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260417T203000Z
UID:https://iub.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12165652
DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Collegiate Recovery Community\n\nJoin us for the CR
 C Week Celebration as we come together to recognize the importance of coll
 egiate recovery and the impact it has on student success\, wellness\, and 
 belonging. Collegiate Recovery provides students with supportive\, substan
 ce-free spaces where they can thrive academically\, socially\, and persona
 lly while pursuing their recovery. This celebration is an opportunity for 
 the campus community to learn more about recovery\, reduce stigma\, and sh
 ow support for students in all stages of their journey. Whether you&rsquo\
 ;re part of the recovery community\, an ally\, or simply curious\, you&rsq
 uo\;re invited to celebrate with us. Enjoy free food\, yard games\, and CR
 C swag while connecting with others and celebrating recovery\, resilience\
 , and community
LOCATION:Wellness House Lawn
URL:https://iub.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12165652
X-SOURCE:IU beINvolved Student Orgs
END:VEVENT
