SUMMARY:We're Crankie: Crankie Festival
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260418T040000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260419T035959Z
UID:event-58103@visitbloomington.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://assets.simpleviewinc.com/simpleview/imag
 e/upload/crm/bloomington/c5_E17260B7-D29E-2C37-47668B18BB006BD6_e1744af3-f
 4a5-8e96-d1978e55c23b3e04.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Bloomington's first ever crankie fest\, celebrating the old ar
 t form of crankies. Come see a performance of crankies! A crankie is a for
 m of storytelling. Using a box with dowel rods to attach and crank (turn) 
 a scroll. Usually accompanied by music or poetry\, with the imagery on the
  scroll. A scroll can be as long as the artist wants. The box of a crankie
  can range in size from a matchbox to as large as you can imagine.
LOCATION:Downtown Library Auditorium
URL:https://www.visitbloomington.com/event/were-crankie%3a-crankie-festiva
 l/58103/
X-SOURCE:Visit Bloomington
END:VEVENT
