SUMMARY:Weed Wrangle at Amy Weingartner Branigin Peninsula Preserve
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260418T100000
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260418T120000
UID:3bcfde7b83a32c4385537ebfeb0dd515@sycamorelandtrust.org
DESCRIPTION:Join Sycamore Land Trust for a volunteer workday at the beauti
 ful Amy Weingartner Branigan Peninsula Preserve! We&#8217\;ll be pulling a
 nd bagging garlic mustard\, an invasive plant that threatens native wildfl
 owers and forest ecosystems by outcompeting them for resources. Removing t
 his aggressive species helps restore balance to the habitat\, giving nativ
 e plants and wildlife a chance to thrive.
LOCATION:Amy Weingartner Branigin Peninsula Preserve
URL:https://sycamorelandtrust.org/2025/03/weed-wrangle-at-amy-weingartner-
 branigin-peninsula-preserve/
