DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Indiana University Guitar Club\n\nReady to plug in 
 and play? Join us for Riff Off!\, a high-energy\, hands-on electric guitar
  workshop where you&rsquo\;ll learn iconic rock riffs in a fun\, supportiv
 e environment. No gear? No problem. We provide the guitars\, pedals\, cabl
 es - everything you need to show up and play. Open to all skill levels\, t
 his event is perfect whether you&rsquo\;re brand new to electric guitar or
  ready to crank up your tone and refine your sound. Come explore distortio
 n\, stage-ready riffs\, and connect with fellow guitarists across campus.
