X-SOURCE-URLS:{"IU beINvolved Student Orgs": "https://iub.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12166185"}
X-SOURCE-ID:iu_campuslabs
SUMMARY:T-Break Workshop
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260421T213000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260421T223000Z
UID:https://iub.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12166185
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://se-images.campuslabs.com/clink/images/4e
 5075c4-a0c1-46bb-b8c6-a4b9223e81dfdd917b87-f696-4223-b327-eb2196714f10.png
DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Collegiate Recovery Community\n\nCurious about taki
 ng a break from cannabis or wanting to better understand your relationship
  with it? Join us for an interactive T-Break Workshop based on the T-Break
  Guide by Tom Fontana. This session explores what a 21-day cannabis tolera
 nce break can look like and offers practical tools for navigating common e
 xperiences like cravings\, sleep changes\, mood shifts\, and stress. Parti
 cipants will learn about the physical\, emotional\, and reflective themes 
 that often come up during a T-Break\, engage in guided discussion\, and ex
 plore strategies for creating balance &mdash\; whether your goal is to res
 et your tolerance\, take a short pause\, or simply reflect on your use. Th
 is workshop is supportive\, educational\, and judgment-free. No prior expe
 rience with a T-Break is required.
LOCATION:The Wellness House
URL:https://iub.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12166185
X-SOURCE:IU beINvolved Student Orgs
END:VEVENT
