X-SOURCE-ID:visitbloomington
SUMMARY:Earth Connection Film Festival
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260422T040000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260423T035959Z
UID:event-58151@visitbloomington.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://assets.simpleviewinc.com/simpleview/imag
 e/upload/crm/bloomington/Earth-Connection-Film-Festival_1F02686C-0F99-5DCB
 -D70C1E5712D8C0A5_1f2d9058-f330-5018-22e6be85dcd0b2c5.png
DESCRIPTION:The Earth Connection Film Festival features innovative environ
 mental films capturing hope\, responsibility\, and interdependence to the 
 Earth with artistry\, innovation\, and soul. From Canadian birdwatchers to
  farmers in Chad\, this free international short film contest unleashes th
 e power of storytelling to address environmental crises. The festival blen
 ds science and the arts to tackle our greatest environmental threat yet: h
 ow we view and respond to the challenges we face.
LOCATION:IU Cinema
URL:https://www.visitbloomington.com/event/earth-connection-film-festival/
 58151/
X-SOURCE:Visit Bloomington
END:VEVENT
