SUMMARY:Union Board Live from Bloomington presents: Magdalena Bay in Conce
 rt
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260422T233000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260423T013000Z
UID:https://iub.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12220287
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://se-images.campuslabs.com/clink/images/c9
 803f6b-a4b3-4d73-96c1-23498dd28b1ac18ed90a-a604-4e97-90a0-06a7cb28acab.png
DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Indiana Memorial Union Board\n\nIU Auditorium\, Uni
 on Board\, and IU Student Foundation are proud to present Magdalena Bay as
  they bring their kaleidoscopic pop universe to the IU Auditorium stage on
 &nbsp\; April 22&nbsp\; for this year's Little 500 concert. The Los Angele
 s&ndash\;based duo of Mica Tenenbaum and Matthew Lewin is known for infect
 ious hooks\, synth-heavy beats\, and a wildly immersive pop sound that&rsq
 uo\;s made them a must-see live act. Make plans to join in for a night of 
 futuristic pop\, high-energy visuals\, and songs that get stuck in your he
 ad immediately to celebrate Little 500 week! Look out in your email for a 
 special code to get your student tickets on Feb 11.&nbsp\; Tickets will op
 en to the general public on Friday\, February 13. Visit here for more info
 rmation. All Indiana University events\, groups\, activities\, and educati
 onal\, cultural\, and historical observances welcome all IU students and o
 ther members of the Indiana University community.
LOCATION:IU Auditorium
URL:https://iub.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12220287
X-SOURCE:IU beINvolved Student Orgs
END:VEVENT
