 e Wellness Week with a refreshing spin at Pedal &amp\; Pours. Join us for 
 a laid-back afternoon centered on movement\, hydration\, and a little Hoos
 ier nostalgia. We&rsquo\;ll be serving up ice-cold water (because wellness
  is the vibe) while we screen the classic cycling film Breaking Away. Whet
 her you&rsquo\;re a seasoned cyclist\, a casual rider\, or just here for t
 he good company\, this event is all about taking a pause\, filling your cu
 p (literally)\, and enjoying a feel-good story about determination\, frien
 dship\, and chasing big dreams on two wheels. Stop by\, grab a pour\, sett
 le in\, and coast into the afternoon with us.
