X-SOURCE-ID:sycamore_land_trust
SUMMARY:Preserve-a-Preserve: Weed Wrangle at Beanblossom Bottoms Nature Pr
 eserve
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260424T100000
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260424T120000
UID:ef90a29be22ef407407b7d80f15a02dd@sycamorelandtrust.org
DESCRIPTION:Spend a day tromping through wetlands during our Beanblossom B
 ottoms Nature Preserve Weed Wrangle as we work together to remove invasive
  cattails. Over the past couple of years\, storms and tornado damage have 
 opened the canopy in parts of the preserve\, allowing more sunlight to rea
 ch the wetlands\, which causes aggressive species like cattails to spread.
LOCATION:Beanblossom Bottoms Nature Preserve
URL:https://sycamorelandtrust.org/2026/03/preserve-a-preserve-weed-wrangle
 -at-beanblossom-bottoms-nature-preserve-2/
