 7e119b-4ef5-4cd9-8069-cc36dfbc83d6626d1262-2cfe-4e91-ad81-e984e1f97164.png
DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Heping (Peace) Chinese Theater Club \n\nDrama &amp\
 ; Dubbing Night is a creative performance event combining a short play and
  live dubbing performances. Part 1: Short Play &ndash\; &ldquo\;Different 
 Species&rdquo\; A 30-minute original short play directed by Getty. The pla
 y explores relationships and perspectives across differences through drama
 tic storytelling. Part 2: Live Dubbing Performances Open-format dubbing sh
 owcase. Participants can perform voice-overs for scenes from films\, anime
 \, games\, or other media of their own creation and edition. All languages
  are welcome. We provide basic microphones and technical support. This eve
 nt encourages cross-cultural expression\, multilingual creativity\, and co
 llaborative performance. Open to all students.
LOCATION:IMU Frangipani Room
URL:https://iub.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12324697
