BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"IU beINvolved Student Orgs": "https://iub.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12066440"}
X-SOURCE-ID:iu_campuslabs
SUMMARY:ASIU Meeting
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260428T000000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260428T010000Z
UID:https://iub.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12066440
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://se-images.campuslabs.com/clink/images/a7
 375cd6-5323-452f-b47a-6d32bc1e5cbe1e5da3c3-3025-4e99-8577-faa0046302e8.png
DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Advocates for Science at IU\n\nAdvoates for Science
  at IU will host monthly in-person meetings for all undergraduate and grad
 uate student members. During these meetings\, we will facilitate discussio
 ns about current club events\, updates\, and opportunities. Additionally\,
  beyond these discussions\, the respective committees within ASIU (politic
 al action\, media outreach\, event planning\, and written journalism) will
  meet in order to collaborate on organization action items and plan for fu
 ture initiatives. This meeting is going to be a necessary and consistent o
 pportunity for all student members of ASIU to meet in person\, discuss the
  most pressing environmental and scientific policy issues at the time\, an
 d work together on building new ideas for both personal development and br
 oader action. In other words\, this meeting will be a forum for discussion
