 35a2a7-851b-4a8f-96c5-ac356ae58944a29bcfb0-a34d-44af-b946-095dfaecdd73.png
DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Counseling and Psychological Services (CAPS)\n\nJoi
 n CAPS staff for a low commitment\, all welcome\, introductory Mindfulness
  in nature experience. The focus of Mindfulness in the Meadow is creating 
 a sense of community\, calm\, and practicing self-care. You will have the 
 chance to learn Mindful coping skills to help you feel connected\, regulat
 ed\, and at peace! Join one or many sessions\, as we will have this opport
 unity throughout the summer. A staff member will have a sign with them at 
 the location. If you have any questions\, you can contact CAPS by calling 
 812-855-5711.
