DESCRIPTION:Hosted by: Indiana Memorial Union Board\n\nJoin Union Board fo
 r it's traditional Almost Midnight Breakfast featuring&nbsp\;breakfast fro
 m IHOP\,&nbsp\;live music\, crafts and so much more fun. Enjoy tarot readi
 ngs\, a chance to by hypnotized by a world renowned hypnotist\, and more. 
 Also get a chance to meet IU faculty and staff who are rooting for your su
 ccess in finals. &nbsp\;RSVP for faster check-in! RSVP does not guarantee 
 you will have breakfast at your arrival time. Time slots are allotted at t
 he door\, first come\, first serve. Get here early and enjoy the activitie
 s before your breakfast time slot or get an early time slot when you arriv
 e and stay after to play. All Indiana University events\, groups\, activit
 ies\, and educational\, cultural\, and historical observances welcome all 
 IU students and other members of the Indiana University community.
