X-SOURCE-ID:visitbloomington
SUMMARY:Spring Plant Sale
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260502T040000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260503T035959Z
UID:event-58223@visitbloomington.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://assets.simpleviewinc.com/simpleview/imag
 e/upload/crm/bloomington/Sycamore-Spring-Plant-Sale-2026-1080-x-1080_B08F3
 937-9024-45A7-2C40395F07979839_b0c3dab1-f6de-c4a4-15d9f38545af6c79.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Sycamore Land Trust is thrilled to announce our fifth annual S
 pring Plant Sale! We are offering over 40 species of plants that were home
 grown in our Native Plant Nursery from seed to plant plug. Many species ar
 e grown from locally collected seed at nearby preserves. All species are e
 thically sourced and native to southern Indiana\, providing benefits to lo
 cal pollinators and wildlife. Plants sell at $4 an individual with all pro
 ceeds going back into nursery operations and native plant restoration
LOCATION:Bloomingfoods East parking lot
URL:https://www.visitbloomington.com/event/spring-plant-sale/58223/
X-SOURCE:Visit Bloomington
END:VEVENT
