CREATED:20260306T125958Z
DESCRIPTION:You are invited to come out to our land and celebrate with us. 
 This year marks 50 years of our community in existence. \nWe are sending ou
 t a "save the date" Evite soon\,  and are looking for some of our "old time
 r original folks."\nCamping if you want. Spots will be delegated.\nSaturday
  evening~ potluck dinner around 6pm \, live music\, bonfire\, and ripping f
 abric for our May Pole.\n\nSunday morning begins with a 9:00 am short medit
 ation and yoga. Potluck breakfast and we will have some hot dishes. A puppe
 t show\, parade\, hikes\, and coronation of the 2026 May day King & Queen. 
 We will have archives and a memorial table\, games\, and much joy to share 
 with you. This is a by-invite event\, but we hope to reach all our family o
 f friends \n\n\nhttps://www.facebook.com/events/25086248954388148/
LAST-MODIFIED:20260306T130000Z
LOCATION:8755 S Rockport Rd\, Bloomington\, IN 47403-9163\, United States
