SUMMARY:Parents' Afternoon In at the Eskenazi Museum of Art
DESCRIPTION:Parents' Afternoon In offers a unique opportunity to enjoy th
 e museum with separate parallel programming that supports creativity\, an
 d relaxation. Kids will have the opportunity to engage with art while par
 ents relax with a variety of activities.  K-12 Children's Program12:00–
 12:30 PM: Guided gallery exploration.  12:30–2:00 PM: Hands-on art acti
 vity in the art studio + snack.  Adult Program12:00–1:00 PM: Experience
  select galleries through a fun and casual guided experience.  1:00–2:0
 0 PM: Choose your own adventure: relax with art-filled coloring sheets\, 
 have a snack from the museum cafe or explore more of the galleries at you
 r leisure.
